# Recurring items (profile/memory/recurring_items.md)

Patterns Reviewer should not flag as anomalies on first sight, even when
they exceed the materiality threshold. Add entries as you accumulate
experience with your data.

Format:

```
- <YYYY-MM>: <short description>. Reason it's expected: <one sentence>.
  Threshold: <USD amount or %>. Approved by: <CFO / Controller>.
```

